items.title: PHOENIX INVESTORS ACQUIRES 1.5 MILLION-SQUARE-FOOT INDUSTRIAL COMPLEX IN CORSICANA, TX
items.description: An affiliate of Phoenix Investors ("Phoenix") announced the acquisition of a large industrial complex located at 2200 South Business 45 in Corsicana, Texas. The property adds approximately 1.5 million square feet across a 172-acre site to Phoenix's portfolio, bringing the Milwaukee-based commercial real estate firm's holdings to over 82 million square feet nationwide.
